  "keyFeatures": [
    "Semantic code knowledge graph backed by tree-sitter AST parsing across 33+ languages stored in local SQLite",
    "Single MCP tool call replaces dozens of file-read tool calls for symbol lookups, call graphs, and impact analysis",
    "9 pluggable semantic search engines including TurboQuant (20-30x embedding compression) and TurboVec (Rust/SIMD)",
    "Persistent cross-session memory with conflict detection, stale review, and symbol-linked observations",
    "Reachability-aware security analysis: determines if vulnerable dependency code is actually reachable from entry points",
    "Architecture layer detection with coupling metrics (Ca/Ce/instability) and snapshot diffing",
    "Auto-detects and integrates with 35 MCP-capable tools (Cursor, Claude Code, Copilot, Windsurf, Cline, and more)",
    "Token optimization: shell compression (60-90% savings), prose compression (Caveman mode), and file read caching",
    "LLM wiki (Karpathy-style) for compounding knowledge across sessions",
    "100% local — no API keys, no external services, nothing leaves your machine"
  ],
  "publicApiSurface": [
